fields.name: Outdoor 2-Person Double Door Camping Dome Tent
fields.description: The 2-Person Double Door Camping Dome Tent is perfect for weekend camping and outdoor adventures. The dome is made of 180T silver coated polyester and 180T polyester taffeta, which is breathable, tear-resistant, and UV-proof. The floor uses strong and durable 210D nylon oxford. Glass fiber poles feature high-strength while remaining lightweight. What's more, the door features double layers, allowing you to zip up mesh only for ventilation or zip up the polyester layer for complete closure. A rainfly over the door provides extra protection against sun and rain.

fields.name: 3-4 Person Camouflage Camping Dome Tent
fields.description: Enjoy entertainment outdoors with the 3-4 Person Camping Dome Tent! It has a spacious room that can sleep up to 4 persons. The dome is made of 180T silver coated polyester, which is breathable, tear-resistant, and UV-proof. Meanwhile, the floor uses strong and waterproof nylon oxford. Glass fiber poles feature high-strength while remaining lightweight. And it can be packed into the included portable bag for ease of transportation. For weekend camping or outdoor adventures, this tent is definitely a great choice. Don't hesitate to order now!

fields.name: Waterproof Outdoor 3-4 Person Automatic Camping Tent
fields.description: This automatic family tent is a great choice for camping, hiking, traveling and other outdoor activities. It has double door and double window. Small compact and lightweight enough to be carried in your backpack. Unique design make it easy to setup and pack-up. You can use it for camping even on rainy days or sunny days. Spider foot structure makes the tent more stable in the windy and rainy weather. Don't hesitate, this tent will make a perfect camping for your family.

fields.name: Peregrine Tent-Gannet 2 Person Combo
fields.description: This is a straight forward, durable tent designed to handle the rigors of long term use.  Great for beginner or intermediate campers, the no frills design combined with a solid construction, YKK zippers, and aluminum poles guarantee years of dependable use.  Two peak vents help keep the tent comfortable and dry in humid conditions. It has 2 doors, 2 side mesh pockets, and a hook at the tent apex.

fields.name: Truck Tent
fields.description: Create the ultimate camping oasis wherever your truck takes you.  No more searching for a clean, dry, and level campsite.  The Sportz Truck Tent assembles in the back of your open bed pickup creating the perfect campsite no matter where you park.  Don't worry about cleaning the truck bed before using the tent, Napier's exclusive full floor design protects you from a dirty truck.

fields.name: 6 Person Big House Deluxe Tent (Big Agnes)
fields.description: This Deluxe 6 Person tent will definitely make you feel like home in the great outdoors (especially if you are less than 6 people sleeping inside). It has steep walls and large living space with two doors that will keep the inside ventilated (with only the mesh closed) and can be sealed with storm flippers over the zippers to keep the inside dry in stormy weather. The tent has 12 large interior pockets to keep your stuff organized and even comes with your own front door welcome mat.

fields.name: Settler 15 F Sleeping Bag
fields.description: Sleep and relax in the SETTLER 15 F sleeping bag after an exciting day outdoors. An ideal 3 season sleeping bag for backpacking, camping, mountaineering, expeditions or hiking trips.

fields.name: Camfy 50 Sleeping Bag
fields.description: Made by lining-190T pongee which can provide lasting coziness and a super soft tucked-in comfort. Outer cover with Layer-185T Polyester which provides excellent air permeability prevents dampness.Specially treated cotton adopts unique through-type quilting ensures cotton is distributed and won't part away. EN ISO 23537-1 temperature test: Comfort: 12℃; Limit: 8℃; Extreme: -4℃.Applied with GRS certified recycle Synthetic cotton which provides excellent comfort and is also environmentally friendly.Fit for people within 150cm/59in of shoulder/chest/hip circumference.

fields.name: Camfy 30 Sleeping Bag
fields.description: Outer layer made by high-density Polyester material which's wear-resistant, dust-proof, and dirt-resistant. Filling with premium-quality, Global Recycled Standard certified, recycled synthetic polyester material, which provide incredibly soft.

fields.name: Sleeping Bag Palmetto C006
fields.description: Stay warm, even when the temperature dips to 30 degrees F in this Coleman cool weather sleeping bag with polyester cover and soft tricot fiber blend liner.  The specially-designed, patented zipper system plows fabric away from the zipper to avoid snags, and Fiberlock Construction prevents insulation from shifting, extending the life of your sleeping bag.

fields.name: Camfy P3 Air Sleeping Pad
fields.description: Prevented leakage by using aviation-grade TPU edge pressing process. A C-type structure and one-way valve allow inflation and deflation faster and easier. It takes only 12-15 quick pumps to be fully inflated.3-inch thickness which provides the stability and considerable insulation from ground temperature. Ergonomic design on the back, waist, legs, and ankles according to the curve of the human body, disperses the body pressure and effectively protects all parts of the body.

fields.name: Sleeping Bag Zero Degrees Silverton
fields.description: Turn your next adventure into a luxury trip with the Coleman Silverton sleeping bag, a mummy-style bag that can help keep you warm in temperatures as low as 0 degrees F.  It's constructed with lightweight ColethermA hollow polyester insulation to help keep you warm from top to bottom.  An adjustable hood and special quilting construction surround  your head and body to help eliminate potential cold spots.

fields.name: Coast EAL12 Black/White Emergency Lantern
fields.description: Whether you are going camping or preparing for a winter storm, the EAL12 Lantern is a great compact lantern that because of the split handle can be easily hung on a branch or line. Cycle between high, low, solid red, and flashing red modes to best suit your situation. (4 x AA batteries not included) With Coast?ÇÖs commitment to quality, the EAL12 Lantern is impact resistant, weather resistant and its LEDs are virtually unbreakable. You'd better catch the chance here!

A 12V battery and solar generator can be charged at the same time.

fields.name: Insulated Cooler Tote Bag by True

fields.name: Outdoor lightweight Chair Portable Folding Camping Chair
fields.description: If you're enjoy camping or fishing, you can't miss this Small Camp Chair. This chair features durable, abrasion-resistant . With engineering mechanics design, it's very stable. Moreover, it's also easy to clean. Its small size and foldable design is very convenient for you to bring it outside. You can bring this chair at any place you like. So what are you waiting for? Don't hesitate, just take it home!

fields.name: PACKiT Lunch Bag Cooler 23 L Multicolored
fields.description: Keep perishable groceries fresh and safe while you run errands with this genius cooler shopping bag. The cooling power is built into the base of the bag so there's no need for ice packs to keep items chilled. From the checkout aisle to your kitchen, your meat, dairy, fruits, veggies and frozen foods stay safe so you don't have to stop home to unload them. This grocery cooler bag also offers plenty of room on the top to carry non-perishable items. Perfect for communities with plastic bag bans, this soft cooler bag is an everyday essential.

fields.name: Camp Dutch Oven
fields.description: The Lodge portable camp stove is the pot that does it all.  The flanged lid holds hot coals and inverts for use as a griddle.  The integral legs allow the oven to sit perfectly over hot coals.  The bail handle is for use with a tripod. Includes Camp Dutch Oven Cooking 101 cookbook.

fields.name: Mini Flatpack Grill
fields.description: The Flatpack Uco portable grill and firepit packs compact for easy transportation to the beach, campsite, or barbeque.  It's constructed of stainless steel for durability and easy maintenance.  After a quick 30 second set-up, you're ready to go.  All you need to do to set up this grill is unfold it and place the grates on top.  It has a stable base for safe grilling, and the sides serve as wind breaks for grilling in windy conditions.  It can also be used as a firepit, to help you leave no trace.  Serves 2 to 3 people.

fields.description: Great for camping and the outdoors!  Boil up some water or create some tasty meals with these aluminum pots. fields.name: One Person Peregrine Refuge Lite Hammock
fields.description: For the cost or weight conscious traveler, this hammock is just 15oz. 250 lb capacity. CE Certified climbing carabiners. Hammock made from lightweight 70d nylon. Drawcord storage sack doubles as a storage pocket  for your book, tablet, or smart phone while lounging.

fields.name: Mobile Dog Gear Dogssentials Drawstring Cinch Sack
fields.description: Mobile Dog Gear's Dogssentials travel drawstring sack will allow you to bring both you and your dog's essentials with you while on the go! Drawstring backpack features include: Easy drawstring cinch closure, carabiner loop, large pocket that fits your dog's frisbee, durable drawstring straps, waste bag dispenser, deep side pockets for water bottles and large mesh front pocket for your phone, keys and wallet. The top completely cinches closed so you won't have to worry about items falling out. There is a heavy duty handle loop so you can hang up your dog bag as soon as you walk through the door. We've also taken away the worry of searching around the bottom of the bag for waste bags. The convenient waste bag dispenser is located at the bottom side of the bag, so you can simply reach around while walking and grab the waste bags and you are good to go! This walking bag is made with durable ballistic fabric which is resistant to ripping and tearing. The heavy duty drawstrings are reinforced with metal grommets. The lightweight fabric won't weigh you down, making it perfect for long walks or even hiking! No more lugging around heavy bags or backpacks that will leave your arms and back aching. This dog bag is perfect for carrying essentials such as water bottles, dog toys, doggy bags, leash and all of your must have items!
